<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>üîê MoneySquad ‚Äì Temporary Password</title>
<style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f8fafc;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, sans-serif;
    }
    .email-container {
      max-width: 500px;
      margin: auto;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      padding: 30px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .header h2 {
      margin: 0;
      color: #4a5568;
    }
    .message {
      font-size: 15px;
      color: #2d3748;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .credential-box {
      background: #f1f5f9;
      border-radius: 6px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2d3748;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .value {
      font-family: monospace;
      background: #e2e8f0;
      padding: 6px 10px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 4px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .note {
      font-size: 13px;
      color: #805ad5;
      background: #fdf6ff;
      border-left: 4px solid #d6bcfa;
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 0 6px 6px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #a0aec0;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="email-container">
<div class="header">
<h2>üîê Temporary Password</h2>
</div>
 
    <div class="message">
      Hi <%= name %>,<br><br>
      You recently requested to reset your password on MoneySquad. Use the temporary credentials below to log in:
</div>
 
    <div class="credential-box">
<div>
<div class="label">Username (Email)</div>
<div class="value"><%= email %></div>
</div>
<br>
<div>
<div class="label">Temporary Password</div>
<div class="value"><%= password %></div>
</div>
</div>
 
    <div class="note">
      ‚ö†Ô∏è This password is temporary. Once logged in, please go to your account settings and update your password. You can always request a new one if needed.
</div>
 
    <div class="footer">
      ¬© MoneySquad ¬∑ <a href="https://app.moneysquad.in/login" style="color:#90cdf4;text-decoration:none;">Login Now</a>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>